@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_inopdj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.sin(v2 + 0.28) - (v2 + 0.89 - v1 + 0.71)))
    v2 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.18 * tmp + 0.53)) * (wp.abs(tmp + 0.42) * 0.38))
    v1 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
